  "detailed_description": "Take 6 clueless guest on a walking safari, or roam the wilds by yourself, in a 4000 acre nature reserve.<br>Score points by spotting any of the 20 species of mammals, and try not to get yourself or guests killed.<br>Nearly 40 species of mammals, birds, reptiles fish and insects.<br>25 African tree and shrub species.<br>Lion, leopard, buffalo, elephant, rhinoceros (black and white), hippopotamus, crocodile, cobra and mamba will attack and kill you or your guests if you get too close.<br>Automatic ID system for the mammals.<br><br><strong>Map 1</strong><br>Mixed woodland and open savanna, with rocky outcrops and a central lake<br><br><strong>Map 2</strong><br>Open floodplain, with forest islands and a network of narrow river channels.<br><br><strong>Map 3</strong><br>Arid Kalahari<br><br><strong>Unlockable animals</strong> <br>Score points to unlock Black leopard, White lion and Big tusker elephant",
  "about_the_game": "Take 6 clueless guest on a walking safari, or roam the wilds by yourself, in a 4000 acre nature reserve.<br>Score points by spotting any of the 20 species of mammals, and try not to get yourself or guests killed.<br>Nearly 40 species of mammals, birds, reptiles fish and insects.<br>25 African tree and shrub species.<br>Lion, leopard, buffalo, elephant, rhinoceros (black and white), hippopotamus, crocodile, cobra and mamba will attack and kill you or your guests if you get too close.<br>Automatic ID system for the mammals.<br><br><strong>Map 1</strong><br>Mixed woodland and open savanna, with rocky outcrops and a central lake<br><br><strong>Map 2</strong><br>Open floodplain, with forest islands and a network of narrow river channels.<br><br><strong>Map 3</strong><br>Arid Kalahari<br><br><strong>Unlockable animals</strong> <br>Score points to unlock Black leopard, White lion and Big tusker elephant",
